Class ShutdownNodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uniba.wiai.lspi.util.console.Command
      • de.uniba.wiai.lspi.chord.console.command.ShutdownNodes

  • public class ShutdownNodes
extends Command

    Command to shutdown a number of nodes.

    To get a description of this command type shutdown -help into the console.
